        <div class="border border-black/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
            <div class="faqHeader flex justify-between items-start customMd:items-center">
                <h2 class="text-black text-base font-semibold font-['Plus Jakarta Sans'] leading-[30px]">How long does it take to send money to the USA?</h2>
                <svg class="iconArrow min-w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">                                 <path d="M26.7081 20.7073C26.6152 20.8003 26.5049 20.874 26.3835 20.9244C26.2621 20.9747 26.132 21.0006 26.0006 21.0006C25.8691 21.0006 25.739 20.9747 25.6176 20.9244C25.4962 20.874 25.3859 20.8003 25.2931 20.7073L16.0006 11.4136L6.70806 20.7073C6.52042 20.895 6.26592 21.0004 6.00056 21.0004C5.73519 21.0004 5.4807 20.895 5.29306 20.7073C5.10542 20.5197 5 20.2652 5 19.9998C5 19.7344 5.10542 19.4799 5.29306 19.2923L15.2931 9.29231C15.3859 9.19933 15.4962 9.12557 15.6176 9.07525C15.739 9.02493 15.8691 8.99902 16.0006 8.99902C16.132 8.99902 16.2621 9.02493 16.3835 9.07525C16.5049 9.12557 16.6152 9.19933 16.7081 9.29231L26.7081 19.2923C26.801 19.3852 26.8748 19.4955 26.9251 19.6169C26.9754 19.7383 27.0013 19.8684 27.0013 19.9998C27.0013 20.1312 26.9754 20.2614 26.9251 20.3828C26.8748 20.5041 26.801 20.6144 26.7081 20.7073Z" fill="black"/>                             </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="faqContent mt-4 max-h-0 overflow-hidden">
                <p class="text-black/60 text-mediumFont font-normal">Once the wire transfer is initiated, it takes up to 2 international working days for the recipient to get the money. Saturdays and Sundays are wire transfer holidays. Other international holidays will also affect the time.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-black/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
            <div class="faqHeader flex justify-between items-start customMd:items-center">
                <h2 class="text-black text-base font-semibold font-['Plus Jakarta Sans'] leading-[30px]">How much tax do I have to pay while sending money to the US?</h2>
                <svg class="iconArrow min-w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">                                 <path d="M26.7081 20.7073C26.6152 20.8003 26.5049 20.874 26.3835 20.9244C26.2621 20.9747 26.132 21.0006 26.0006 21.0006C25.8691 21.0006 25.739 20.9747 25.6176 20.9244C25.4962 20.874 25.3859 20.8003 25.2931 20.7073L16.0006 11.4136L6.70806 20.7073C6.52042 20.895 6.26592 21.0004 6.00056 21.0004C5.73519 21.0004 5.4807 20.895 5.29306 20.7073C5.10542 20.5197 5 20.2652 5 19.9998C5 19.7344 5.10542 19.4799 5.29306 19.2923L15.2931 9.29231C15.3859 9.19933 15.4962 9.12557 15.6176 9.07525C15.739 9.02493 15.8691 8.99902 16.0006 8.99902C16.132 8.99902 16.2621 9.02493 16.3835 9.07525C16.5049 9.12557 16.6152 9.19933 16.7081 9.29231L26.7081 19.2923C26.801 19.3852 26.8748 19.4955 26.9251 19.6169C26.9754 19.7383 27.0013 19.8684 27.0013 19.9998C27.0013 20.1312 26.9754 20.2614 26.9251 20.3828C26.8748 20.5041 26.801 20.6144 26.7081 20.7073Z" fill="black"/>                             </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="faqContent mt-4 max-h-0 overflow-hidden">
                <p class="text-black/60 text-mediumFont font-normal">All remittance transactions from India are subject to GST. It's less than 1000 INR for amounts up to Rs 10 Lakhs. The exact GST amount to be paid it can be found using the article below;<br>
                <a class="text-red-500" target="_blank" href="https://www.extravelmoney.com/blog/gst-on-foreign-exchange-transactions-in-india/">How Much Tax You've To Pay On Foreign Exchange Transactions In India?</a><br><br>
                Sometimes TCS (Tax collected at source) may be collected on your transaction. It can be reclaimed at the time of filing your IT returns. It's calculated based on the total amount remitted in the current financial year. TCS rate varies with the purpose of your transfer. You can refer our article <a class="text-red-500" target="_blank" href="https://www.extravelmoney.com/blog/tcs-on-money-transfer-from-india-to-abroad-simple-guide/">'TCS on money transfer abroad from India'</a> for a detailed explanation.<br><br>
                You can use our <a class="text-red-500" target="_blank" href="https://www.extravelmoney.com/tools/tcs-calculator-for-foreign-remittances-from-india/">TCS calculator</a> tool to find out the exact amount.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-black/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
            <div class="faqHeader flex justify-between items-start customMd:items-center">
                <h2 class="text-black text-base font-semibold font-['Plus Jakarta Sans'] leading-[30px]">What are the fees and charges associated with money transfers?</h2>
                <svg class="iconArrow min-w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">                                 <path d="M26.7081 20.7073C26.6152 20.8003 26.5049 20.874 26.3835 20.9244C26.2621 20.9747 26.132 21.0006 26.0006 21.0006C25.8691 21.0006 25.739 20.9747 25.6176 20.9244C25.4962 20.874 25.3859 20.8003 25.2931 20.7073L16.0006 11.4136L6.70806 20.7073C6.52042 20.895 6.26592 21.0004 6.00056 21.0004C5.73519 21.0004 5.4807 20.895 5.29306 20.7073C5.10542 20.5197 5 20.2652 5 19.9998C5 19.7344 5.10542 19.4799 5.29306 19.2923L15.2931 9.29231C15.3859 9.19933 15.4962 9.12557 15.6176 9.07525C15.739 9.02493 15.8691 8.99902 16.0006 8.99902C16.132 8.99902 16.2621 9.02493 16.3835 9.07525C16.5049 9.12557 16.6152 9.19933 16.7081 9.29231L26.7081 19.2923C26.801 19.3852 26.8748 19.4955 26.9251 19.6169C26.9754 19.7383 27.0013 19.8684 27.0013 19.9998C27.0013 20.1312 26.9754 20.2614 26.9251 20.3828C26.8748 20.5041 26.801 20.6144 26.7081 20.7073Z" fill="black"/>                             </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="faqContent mt-4 max-h-0 overflow-hidden">
                <p class="text-black/60 text-mediumFont font-normal">There will be a processing bank charge of 354-590 INR, depending on the chosen bank. Along with this, the beneficiary's bank in the US will charge a beneficiary bank charge of 15 to 30 USD. The exact amount can be found by checking with the beneficiary bank in the US. You can add the amount as extra while sending so that the beneficiary receives the exact amount you intend to send. There is an option to pay beneficiary bank charge in INR although we don't recommend this option.<br><br>
                All the fees applicable will be shown transparently on our order summary page and also intimated by our customer support team prior to the transfer. Extravelmoney does not charge any additional fee.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-black/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
