            </div>
            <div class="faqContent mt-4 max-h-0 overflow-hidden">
                <p class="text-black/60 text-mediumFont font-normal">Not required. This is one of the advantages of doing a money transfer via Extravelmoney. Normally banks do remittance transactions only for their account holders. But with Extravelmoney you can do the transfer even if you don't have an account in the chosen bank. If you already have an account in the chosen bank, you can still transfer via Extravelmoney for better rates and service.</p>
