            </div>
            <div class="faqContent mt-4 max-h-0 overflow-hidden">
                <p class="text-black/60 text-mediumFont font-normal">Extravelmoney gets real-time exchange rates from our partner banks and exchange houses. These are exclusive rates for Extravelmoney and are usually much lower than what they offer directly to their customers.<br><br>
                Exchange rates are subject to fluctuations in the market. Exchange rates on the day of transfer will apply to all remittance transactions. We will confirm the exchange rate with you before initiating the transfer. If you are not happy with the day's rate, you can postpone or even cancel the money transfer.</p>
